testsuite.name: com.ze.partner.aplication.controller.PartnerControllerTest

testcase.name: given call valid partner_id then return 200 status code()
given call invalid partner_id then return 404 status code()
given the same partner 2 times then return 409 status code()
given a lat and long valid then return the nearest partner with 200 status code()
given a lat and long valid then return the nearest between 2 partners with 200 status code()
given valid partner then return 201 status code()
